    HtmlGlobalElement<T extends com.k2.XMLBuilder.XMLElement>
    This abstract class is and extension of XMLElement and is the basis for all Html elements except the 'html' element The class defines methods to set the standard html attributes but not the html event attributes
    HtmlPage
    This class defines an HtmlPage instance.
    HtmlPhrasingElement<T extends com.k2.XMLBuilder.XMLElement>
    This abstract class defines phrasing elements This class adds the methods to create the child elements appropriate to phrasing elements
    HtmlPhrasingElementNoTime<T extends com.k2.XMLBuilder.XMLElement>
    This abstract class defines phrasing elements but without the ability to create time elements as child elements This class adds the methods to create the child elements appropriate to phrasing elements
    HtmlRestrictedFlowElement<T extends com.k2.XMLBuilder.XMLElement>
    This abstract element defines a flow element that disallows header, footer and address elements This class adds the methods to create the child elements appropriate to flow elements excluding header, footer and address elements
    HtmlStyledFlowElement<T extends com.k2.XMLBuilder.XMLElement>
    This abstract class defines styled flow elements This class adds the methods to create the child elements appropriate to flow elements plus the style element
    HtmlVeryRestrictedFlowElement<T extends com.k2.XMLBuilder.XMLElement>
    This abstract element defines a flow element that disallows header, footer, address elements, headings and section This class adds the methods to create the child elements appropriate to flow elements excluding header, footer, address, heading and section elements
